# Specification Files

Place your specification markdown files here. Each spec should describe
a topic of concern (feature, component, or capability) derived from a
Job to be Done (JTBD).

## Example Structure

```markdown
# specs/user-authentication.md

## Overview
Brief description of what this feature does.

## Requirements
- Requirement 1
- Requirement 2

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Testable criterion 1
- [ ] Testable criterion 2

## Dependencies
- Backend API: POST /api/auth/login
```
